726385f-a.title: Queens: Cooper Avenue - 59th Street
726385f-a.text:
Cooper Ave., east of 59th Street to Eightieth Ave. (formerly Alden
Ave.) Cooper Avenue veers northeastward in the background. Peaked two
story structure at right background was No. 29 Cooper Ave. (now on
Eightieth Ave.)
May 1923.
Euoene L. Armbruster Collection.
